pageContext.claim: “McCain didn't get the job done for our great vets and the VA, and they knew it. That's why, when I had my dispute with him, I had such incredible support from the vets and from the military. The vets were on my side because I got the job done.”
pageContext.analysis: Sen. John McCain sponsored numerous bills dealing with veterans' care. The bill Trump is referring to when he says "I got the job done" is actually named after McCain.
